in network template  for default gateway

auto lo
iface lo inet loopback
auto eth0
iface eth0 inet static
    address 192.168.1.10
    netmask 255.255.255.0
    network 192.168.1.0
    broadcast 192.168.1.254
    post-up route add default gw 192.168.1.1 metric 1
    pre-down route del default gw 192.168.1.1

auto eth1
iface eth1 inet static
    address 192.168.2.10
    netmask 255.255.255.0
    network 192.168.2.0
    broadcast 192.168.2.254
    post-up route add default gw 192.168.2.1 metric 2
    pre-down route del default gw 192.168.2.1
    
How to add default in redhat /centos


br-vlan defination problem , shd be type should be bridge 
    
in centos epel repo gpg check = 0

Host for LXc as well as KVM both port 22 are closed , Firewall on host is blocking this 





